ation of important aspects of life and thought in the nuclear age.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Public Policy / Economic Policy.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077356263940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773562639423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773562639/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles